<plot>"EXIT 6011 miles" is the story of a married Korean couple, Jun-Woo and Mi-Sun, who are illegal residents in the U.S. Unwilling to live with the economic hardships of their lives, they travel to the top of a mountain for suicide. After they arrive at a forest, they spend their last night together. On the next day, with sadness, they drive up to a cliff of the mountain.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185377</url></doc>
